1
00:05:55,490 --> 00:06:00,740
Today we have assembled here to do the Puja of Vishnumaya.

2
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:13,990
Vishnumaya is created through human effort, also.

3
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:20,910
As you see the clouds, when they rub against each other,

4
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:30,580
then the electricity is created. So first the clouds have to be created.

5
00:06:30,580 --> 00:06:40,280
The sun acts on the sea. See how many chakras come into play.

6
00:06:40,290 --> 00:06:45,290
Sea is the Void, and the sun acts on the sea.

7
00:06:45,330 --> 00:06:54,580
Also the moon acts on the sea. As a result of that, clouds are created.

8
00:06:54,580 --> 00:07:08,410
This electricity is not created in the ocean -- that would create problems.

9
00:07:08,450 --> 00:07:19,410
Is created in the sky so that everybody can see it, can hear it.

10
00:07:19,410 --> 00:07:26,540
They see it first and hear it later.

11
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:33,660
It's all well organized, well calculated. That is Vishnumaya.

12
00:07:33,700 --> 00:07:42,370
But it was created, also, with some understanding

13
00:07:42,370 --> 00:07:47,200
by human beings on this earth. First of all they saw

14
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:53,790
the two clouds rubbing each other.

15
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:57,540
So in the primitive stage, human beings

16
00:07:57,580 --> 00:08:02,410
tried to rub two material things to create electricity.

17
00:08:02,450 --> 00:08:07,740
So two material things, that is two parts of matter,

18
00:08:07,790 --> 00:08:13,990
when rubbed created the electricity. It's very significant to see:

19
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:18,790
matter can be used to create electricity.

20
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:24,490
The spark of the electricity comes from the matter.

21
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:30,240
Without matter, they could not have started cooking the food.

22
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:34,120
So how it has helped the Void.

23
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:40,540
First from the ocean, it went into the sky, gave the message to the people

24
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:44,910
to create the electricity. See the love.

25
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:48,660
Then people learned how to cook the food

26
00:08:48,700 --> 00:09:00,620
for the digestion to be easier for human beings. How it comes back! From nature,

27
00:09:00,660 --> 00:09:02,830
how human beings learn

28
00:09:02,830 --> 00:09:16,410
and do it for the good, betterment, hita, of human beings. This benevolent energy,

29
00:09:16,450 --> 00:09:22,950
which was meant for the benevolence of human beings, again was utilized.

30
00:09:22,990 --> 00:09:28,200
As you see, this is the creation, all this is of Vishnumaya.

31
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:34,580
That's why it's a maya. With electricity you can create a maya,

32
00:09:34,580 --> 00:09:38,660
you know that very well, how you can create it. So many are here,

33
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:43,200
luckily in such a spontaneous way,

34
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:48,290
so many who are dealing with this electricity in creating maya.

35
00:09:48,330 --> 00:09:57,040
America is so much helped by this electricity, by Vishnumaya.

36
00:09:57,040 --> 00:10:00,280
You're not thankful to it.

37
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:04,660
Like you have got Niagara Falls, you have so many falls here.

38
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:08,990
Again, the water when it falls -- it comes from water --

39
00:10:08,990 --> 00:10:20,200
when the water falls on the lower level, very lower level, then it moves the turbine

40
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:23,830
and those movements can create electricity.

41
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:31,240
So you have hydrostatic electricity.

42
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:35,410
Also the electricity is produced, as you know, through coal.

43
00:10:35,450 --> 00:10:43,280
Now here, again, the Mother Earth works out for the betterment

44
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:52,410
of human beings to create the coal in Her being.

45
00:10:52,450 --> 00:10:59,200
I think She must be taking all the baddhas, absorbing all of them in Her stomach,

46
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:04,200
and must be burning the stones inside Her to make the coal.

47
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:10,200
And then that coal is used for making electricity.

48
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:16,870
How much the nature is working for our betterment!

49
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:20,870
Your New York would not have been there but for electricity.

50
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:22,870
It stopped for fifteen minutes

51
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:29,700
and you knew the power of electricity.

52
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:37,990
You cannot move without it. We cannot exist without it. That's why it had to be used and created --

53
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:43,700
given you so much of benevolence. You cook with it; you see with it;

54
00:11:43,740 --> 00:11:49,120
you listen with it; you enjoy with it. You wouldn't have your televisions;

55
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:51,580
you wouldn't have anything without electricity.

56
00:11:51,580 --> 00:11:54,700
You won't even have these "Exits" here written.

57
00:11:54,700 --> 00:11:57,410
You would have walked into the walls.

58
00:11:57,410 --> 00:12:02,540
So much of this Vishnumaya has worked,

59
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:06,450
but She is a Maya. She can create a maya.

60
00:12:06,490 --> 00:12:10,450
And this has created a big maya in the minds of human beings

61
00:12:10,490 --> 00:12:14,280
that we are on top of the world. You're not.

62
00:12:14,290 --> 00:12:24,240
If electricity recedes from you, you'll become again

63
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:30,660
the same primitive people making electricity out of rubbing the stones -- take it from Me.

64
00:12:30,660 --> 00:12:37,240
This flow of electricity is available to you for your good,

65
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:44,540
and not for your destruction. But what has happened today

66
00:12:44,580 --> 00:12:49,370
is that using this electricity for your destruction.

67
00:12:49,370 --> 00:12:54,450
I remember about, say, thirty, forty years back, or even earlier

68
00:12:54,450 --> 00:12:59,990
when we saw the films, they were not colored films, American films

69
00:12:59,990 --> 00:13:06,660
were beautiful films with substance in it. They wouldn't show one married man

70
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:10,160
running after another married woman. None of these stories.

71
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:15,620
Very pure form of beautiful family life.

72
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:20,410
Everything nourishing was shown.

73
00:13:20,450 --> 00:13:28,700
We don't hear of any such thing where they showed evil winning over.

74
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:34,450
Now you find they show a thief, and the thief becomes the hero.

75
00:13:34,490 --> 00:13:41,950
Then the people see those films, and the children especially

76
00:13:41,990 --> 00:13:47,290
I've seen have that thief as the symbol of something great.

77
00:13:47,330 --> 00:13:52,330
So they are going against the Void completely,

78
00:13:52,370 --> 00:13:55,200
against the religion that is within us, absolutely.

79
00:13:55,240 --> 00:14:05,580
The thing that was to nourish the Void, the one that was to sustain you

80
00:14:05,620 --> 00:14:13,160
in your valences, is now disturbing the Void completely.

81
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:17,790
That's the maya part of it - the same electricity

82
00:14:17,830 --> 00:14:23,080
which was to give you the right path, the light in the darkness,

83
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:31,280
is now sucking you in like a magnet towards your destruction.

84
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:39,240
This is the Vishnumaya Who came to this country in such a big way

85
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:45,240
and then spread all over. Has given ideas to everyone.

86
00:14:45,280 --> 00:14:49,830
People picked up all your techniques, all your styles,

87
00:14:49,830 --> 00:14:54,910
I mean you have Hollywood and all these very famous people

88
00:14:54,950 --> 00:14:57,910
here who have thrived on this electricity.

89
00:14:57,910 --> 00:15:04,080
But without thanking the Vishnumaya, they started doing things

90
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:10,540
which were against Vishnumaya. This Vishnumaya is the One Who has helped you

91
00:15:10,580 --> 00:15:14,830
because She is the Sister of Shri Krishna;

92
00:15:14,870 --> 00:15:19,080
and because this is the domain of Shri Krishna, She came down here to help you.

93
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:22,200
Now She's the Sister -- this must be understood very well.

94
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:26,370
Now sisterly relation is a pure relationship.

95
00:15:26,370 --> 00:15:31,410
Now, of course, everything is so confused, but that's the purest relationship

96
00:15:31,450 --> 00:15:34,330
between the brother and the sister.

97
00:15:34,370 --> 00:15:39,410
The brother is protected by sister.

98
00:15:39,410 --> 00:15:50,280
And the sister's chastity is looked after by the brother.

99
00:15:50,290 --> 00:15:52,740
A brother who doesn't feel hurt

100
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:58,620
if his sister chastity is in danger

101
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:02,490
or she plays about with her chastity, he is not a brother.

102
00:16:02,490 --> 00:16:06,240
He is not a brother anymore. He's responsible

103
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:10,080
to see that his sister keeps her chastity.

104
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:15,620
Only her chastity can protect him -- it's a mutual working.

105
00:16:15,660 --> 00:16:23,080
This feeling, if it does not develop that, "She is my sister

106
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:27,040
and that I have to look after her chastity,

107
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,990
for that I have to behave myself well,

108
00:16:28,990 --> 00:16:31,790
so that she doesn't find faults with me."

109
00:16:31,830 --> 00:16:35,410
It's such a cleansing process this relationship has,

110
00:16:35,450 --> 00:16:39,490
as much as the electricity has the cleansing process for you.

111
00:16:39,490 --> 00:16:43,330
Everywhere what the electricity does,

112
00:16:43,330 --> 00:16:47,580
a sister does for her brother -- she cooks for him,

113
00:16:47,620 --> 00:16:54,280
she tells him the right path, she enlightens him and sometimes

114
00:16:54,290 --> 00:17:00,280
shocks him, also. They have to have certain shocks;

115
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:03,450
otherwise they will not know how to work it out.

116
00:17:03,490 --> 00:17:08,200
And the best of all, she's the one for whom you have to be

117
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:13,740
very careful to know the technique how to handle your sister.

118
00:17:13,740 --> 00:17:17,280
If you do not know how to handle your sister,

119
00:17:17,290 --> 00:17:20,330
you can be absolutely wrong

120
00:17:20,370 --> 00:17:26,950
and you may get it -- something that you would never expect to get.

121
00:17:26,990 --> 00:17:31,240
So one must understand how to handle a sister.

122
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:34,990
In this case, we have to know that the same

123
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:41,200
was born again at the time of Shri Krishna as Draupadi.

124
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:51,830
She took Her birth as Draupadi. And when Draupadi was attacked by the Kauravas,

125
00:17:51,830 --> 00:17:57,240
they wanted to remove Her sari.

126
00:17:57,280 --> 00:18:04,740
So remove the sari itself is a symbol that they challenged her chastity.

127
00:18:04,790 --> 00:18:09,040
Now if you see in the Maya Nagri, women have no sense at all

128
00:18:09,040 --> 00:18:14,580
that they should cover this part of their body.

129
00:18:14,620 --> 00:18:17,410
In this Maya Nagri, the other way round.

130
00:18:17,450 --> 00:18:22,080
When I heard the very responsible person saying that, "In our culture,

131
00:18:22,080 --> 00:18:28,540
women must expose their body." What is this culture? Is anti-Krishna,

132
00:18:28,580 --> 00:18:33,540
completely anti-Vishnumaya. Such people

133
00:18:33,540 --> 00:18:40,240
will get into trouble, I'm sure, with electrical problems.

134
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:54,990
The brothers who do not bother about the chastity of the husband of their sister,

135
00:18:55,040 --> 00:19:06,740
and also supporting and asking to do wrong things, hide his things,

136
00:19:06,740 --> 00:19:15,450
are also equally responsible. Like in Sahaja Yoga, you know

137
00:19:15,490 --> 00:19:20,790
that a sister is to be protected; and the sister husband,

138
00:19:20,830 --> 00:19:25,580
if he's doing anything wrong, he's to be told off by the brother.

139
00:19:25,620 --> 00:19:32,540
Like once in India, one newspaper passed some remarks about Me.

140
00:19:32,540 --> 00:19:36,240
My brothers were up in arms. I thought,

141
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:38,790
"Now, it's going to be terrible. How am I to manage it?"

142
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:44,700
It was a big, strong ... They were going to go to the courts. When I told them, "I'll not go to the courts."

143
00:19:44,740 --> 00:19:46,410
"All right, don't go. But we'll go."

144
00:19:46,410 --> 00:19:49,700
They told My husband also. My husband and My brothers put together,

145
00:19:49,740 --> 00:19:53,700
it was formidable! I didn't know what to do.

146
00:19:53,740 --> 00:19:58,620
I wrote to one Sahaja Yogi that, "Go and see the editor of the newspaper.

147
00:19:58,620 --> 00:20:00,200
Tell him that these are My brothers,

148
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:05,700
be careful. They are very powerful people in India and from here My husband. It's terrible."

149
00:20:05,740 --> 00:20:11,620
But they would not apologize. So I thought of another Vishnumaya

150
00:20:11,660 --> 00:20:21,740
that there was a big strike and the paper was closed for exactly six months.

151
00:20:21,740 --> 00:20:28,580
And they had to go in for a big, very big losses. And when they started,

152
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:33,620
the people who were working there came back and said that,

153
00:20:33,660 --> 00:20:38,200
"Why did you write against Shri Mataji? We're not going to come back."

154
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:41,200
And they had to apologize.

155
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:47,990
So how the brother's love can compel even Adi Shakti

156
00:20:47,990 --> 00:20:55,240
to do things that She would not normally do. In the same way,

157
00:20:55,280 --> 00:21:01,410
when Draupadi was challenged, Shri Krishna was not in Hastinapur

158
00:21:01,410 --> 00:21:11,240
where it happened. He was thousand, at least more than thousand miles away from that place.

159
00:21:11,280 --> 00:21:21,240
He said that, "Shankha chakra gada padma, garuda lai sidhare."

160
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:28,790
He came on His condor with all His weapons -- shankha, chakra, gada, padma.

161
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:35,120
All these He brought to save the chastity of His Sister.

162
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:37,870
There are many incidents in our history,

163
00:21:37,910 --> 00:21:43,990
I don't know if I can cite anything in your history. But I would say

164
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:48,910
when I see Abraham Lincoln I think he was a great brother

165
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:56,870
to the Statue of Liberty. The way he fought for women

166
00:21:56,910 --> 00:22:01,540
in such pure love and without taking any money,

167
00:22:01,580 --> 00:22:13,950
without charging them anything, to punish the husbands who were drunkards.

168
00:22:13,950 --> 00:22:19,330
That's just like a very good, powerful brother to behave.

169
00:22:19,370 --> 00:22:24,870
But those feelings are now dying out I think.

170
00:22:24,910 --> 00:22:34,160
But say in Russia, when I went, went to see Lenin's house and through out,

171
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:39,240
apart from his wife, was his sister who helped him --

172
00:22:39,280 --> 00:22:43,870
to type for him, to do all his official work.

173
00:22:43,910 --> 00:22:51,410
He has written volumes and volumes of books in that small age

174
00:22:51,410 --> 00:22:53,950
of fifty-four years, volumes!

175
00:22:53,990 --> 00:22:58,080
First of all he was in Siberia and just imagine,

176
00:22:58,080 --> 00:23:02,160
this sister of his has typed most of it.

177
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:08,910
Throughout in the whole tour, we felt the presence of the sister

178
00:23:08,910 --> 00:23:12,450
and the way she has helped her brother.

179
00:23:12,450 --> 00:23:18,660
This relationship is so pure which doesn't want anything.

180
00:23:18,700 --> 00:23:23,410
A wife may say that, "If you don't give me a coat, I'll divorce you."

181
00:23:23,450 --> 00:23:26,910
May in England and possibly in America they say so.

182
00:23:26,950 --> 00:23:32,990
But a sister cannot divorce. She cannot divorce.

183
00:23:32,990 --> 00:23:37,950
This time in the newspaper, they published the name of My brother.

184
00:23:37,990 --> 00:23:41,870
So I said, "What can I do? He's My brother, so he's My brother."

185
00:23:41,870 --> 00:23:50,580
Good, bad, anything, he's My brother, I cannot divorce.

186
00:23:50,620 --> 00:23:57,120
It's something, a relationship which you cannot break.

187
00:23:57,160 --> 00:24:01,240
Nature has given you this relationship.

188
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:05,450
But when you come to the collective, it's very important

189
00:24:05,490 --> 00:24:14,200
that we must respect this relationship. If you do not respect this relationship,

190
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:21,490
you cannot work out collectively. Like in a party I go

191
00:24:21,540 --> 00:24:25,830
and I feel something very funny happening.

192
00:24:25,870 --> 00:24:31,910
Somebody's wife is entangled with somebody's husband.

193
00:24:31,950 --> 00:24:36,580
All sorts of funny things happen. But in collective

194
00:24:36,620 --> 00:24:40,910
if you know, except for my wife the rest of them are my sisters.

195
00:24:40,950 --> 00:24:42,990
The purity settles in like that,

196
00:24:43,040 --> 00:24:46,790
you don't have to worry. They're my sisters.

197
00:24:46,790 --> 00:24:52,580
And your eyes steady out.

198
00:24:52,580 --> 00:24:56,160
Innocence starts pouring out of your eyes.

199
00:24:56,200 --> 00:25:03,080
It's a very, very simple thing. So in the eye, when you get your Realization,

200
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:06,990
you get a glint -- must have seen, there's a shine

201
00:25:06,990 --> 00:25:12,950
that is Vishnumaya. That is the Vishnumaya which shines through your eyes.

202
00:25:12,950 --> 00:25:17,950
And She's the One Who makes you through the maya of Vishnumaya.

203
00:25:17,990 --> 00:25:23,040
This glint in the eye you must have seen in people who are realized souls

204
00:25:23,080 --> 00:25:33,330
and this glint in the eye is the one that makes you understand and feel the beauty

205
00:25:33,330 --> 00:25:40,370
and the power of sisterly/brotherly relationship.

206
00:25:40,410 --> 00:25:48,950
In the beginning of Sahaja Yoga, I found it impossible to establish this.

207
00:25:48,950 --> 00:25:57,790
So I said, "Let's try the Vishnumaya." And it worked.

208
00:25:57,830 --> 00:26:01,620
Actually, naturally we know this is wrong.

209
00:26:01,620 --> 00:26:05,620
We know that it is wrong, naturally.

210
00:26:05,660 --> 00:26:08,280
We don't have to have a law for it.

211
00:26:08,290 --> 00:26:13,280
One lady come to America with her brother and she told Me

212
00:26:13,280 --> 00:26:16,370
when I had not come to America, "It's a funny place."

213
00:26:16,410 --> 00:26:20,620
She said, "I went to America and we wanted to stay in one room",

214
00:26:20,660 --> 00:26:23,660
because they wanted to save some money. They said, "No. If you are brothers

215
00:26:23,660 --> 00:26:28,620
and sisters, you can't stay." She said, "Why? I mean in India

216
00:26:28,660 --> 00:26:31,080
if you are brother and sister you can always stay.

217
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:38,700
If you are not brother and sister, then of course you can't stay, you don't stay together,

218
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:41,660
the other way round. If you are brother and sister

219
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:45,290
you cannot stay in one room in a hotel under law.

220
00:26:45,330 --> 00:26:50,330
And it's a father and a daughter you can't stay in one room.

221
00:26:50,370 --> 00:26:55,540
Absurd. I mean for us Indians it's a shock. I said, "But why?"

222
00:26:55,540 --> 00:26:58,910
I just couldn't understand. Now I know what it is,

223
00:26:58,950 --> 00:27:02,950
that it has become now a law to that extent.

224
00:27:02,990 --> 00:27:06,620
To us, it is absurd to have such a law.

225
00:27:06,620 --> 00:27:10,280
And, as we have learned so many things from you

226
00:27:10,290 --> 00:27:14,540
about electricity, you also better learn from us certain thing

227
00:27:14,540 --> 00:27:18,330
about Vishnumaya's powers.

228
00:27:18,370 --> 00:27:21,830
There's no harm in learning something for the roots,

229
00:27:21,870 --> 00:27:24,910
because if the tree has gone wrong,

230
00:27:24,910 --> 00:27:29,790
it has to learn something very much essential from the roots and that is it,

231
00:27:29,830 --> 00:27:34,160
the purity of relationship between brothers and sisters.

232
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:36,370
The sister relationship

233
00:27:36,410 --> 00:27:45,370
always gives a very big cementing force for the husband and wife.

234
00:27:45,410 --> 00:27:49,240
I know if My husband tries to trouble Me,

235
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:52,950
his own sister will be after his life.

236
00:27:52,950 --> 00:27:58,580
And he'd better be careful about it and same with Me.

237
00:27:58,620 --> 00:28:05,660
If I do anything wrong, My brother will side with My husband and not with Me.

238
00:28:05,700 --> 00:28:09,120
So it cements the relationships very well.

239
00:28:09,120 --> 00:28:15,580
In the history that I know of two very beautiful incidents I'll tell you

240
00:28:15,580 --> 00:28:21,200
which come to My mind today is one of Shivaji.

241
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:27,370
When Shivaji -- it's twice it has happened in his lifetime which is very remarkable.

242
00:28:27,410 --> 00:28:34,490
He was once presented with a lady, was very beautiful.

243
00:28:34,540 --> 00:28:42,330
And people had plundered her things and all her ornaments,

244
00:28:42,370 --> 00:28:49,160
because she was a daughter of a Muslim courtesan,

245
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:54,490
as you call the courtier. And they tried to plunder him

246
00:28:54,490 --> 00:29:03,790
and they brought this beautiful woman before Shivaji. So Shivaji looked at her and said,

247
00:29:03,790 --> 00:29:10,280
"Please remove your veil", because Muslims have a veil.

248
00:29:10,290 --> 00:29:18,160
And when she removed her veil, he said that, "If my mother was as beautiful as you are,

249
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:24,370
I would have been equally beautiful." What a thing to say - what a poetic thing to say!

250
00:29:24,370 --> 00:29:26,620
That is that, "If you were my mother,

251
00:29:26,660 --> 00:29:29,580
I would have been as beautiful as you are",

252
00:29:29,580 --> 00:29:34,120
means you are my sister.

253
00:29:34,120 --> 00:29:36,490
And then he got very angry with all these people

254
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:38,830
and he asked them that, "You'd better take her away

255
00:29:38,870 --> 00:29:42,450
and never do such a thing to any woman." And not only,

256
00:29:42,490 --> 00:29:45,790
but he gave lots of ornaments and lots of things to her

257
00:29:45,830 --> 00:29:48,540
to say that she's a sister

258
00:29:48,540 --> 00:29:51,620
going to the husband with all respect and regard.

259
00:29:51,660 --> 00:30:00,870
And this gentleman, her husband, was a very deadly enemy of Shivaji.

260
00:30:00,910 --> 00:30:10,410
How he solved the problem with such purity and then this gentleman

261
00:30:10,450 --> 00:30:15,200
become sort of a milder person with this gesture of his.

262
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:20,910
Second in his lifetime we hear about a fort

263
00:30:20,910 --> 00:30:27,620
which is now very close to My house in Pune was, there was a Rajput lady

264
00:30:27,660 --> 00:30:31,490
called Kamal Kumari, who was entrapped by the man

265
00:30:31,540 --> 00:30:39,160
who was the officer of that fort, who was a Muslim.

266
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:43,870
And he was telling this Kamal Kumari that, "You must marry me." And she would not accept.

267
00:30:43,910 --> 00:30:50,330
They had brought her from somewhere sort of by force. And she would not accept;

268
00:30:50,330 --> 00:30:56,620
she was Rajput. And he said, "By tomorrow, you'll have to marry me."

269
00:30:56,660 --> 00:31:06,620
This lady didn't know what to do, so with someone very secretly

270
00:31:06,620 --> 00:31:11,120
she sent a letter to Shivaji with a rakhi.

271
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:17,790
But it reached the mother of Shivaji.

272
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:27,830
Mother sent a letter, sent a message, to Shivaji on a horse that, "Come here as fast as possible --

273
00:31:27,830 --> 00:31:31,120
if you're eating your food, then come here to wash your hands"

274
00:31:31,120 --> 00:31:35,700
to that extent. And Shivaji was so obedient to his mother,

275
00:31:35,740 --> 00:31:40,620
very obedient. One has to learn from his character.

276
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:47,540
He rushed there, because obedience was his power.

277
00:31:47,580 --> 00:31:51,240
He rushed there and asked, "Mother, what is it?"

278
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:54,790
She said, "No, I want to play chess with you."

279
00:31:54,830 --> 00:31:59,910
He said, "Why now?" "I must play chess." He couldn't understand.

280
00:31:59,950 --> 00:32:05,540
And she played chess and she won something. She could have told him,

281
00:32:05,580 --> 00:32:12,280
but she just wanted to sort of put a Vishnumaya on him. He lost.

282
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:15,830
"Mother, what do you want?" She said, "Today

283
00:32:15,870 --> 00:32:22,990
I want you by night to capture this fort."

284
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:33,990
"Today?" "Yes." Then she showed him the letter and the rakhi.

285
00:32:33,990 --> 00:32:38,280
Rakhi was so powerful that a mother had to ask her son,

286
00:32:38,280 --> 00:32:42,290
who was responsible for the deliverance of Maharashtra

287
00:32:42,330 --> 00:32:51,330
from the clutches of the Muslims, that he should go to this fort and capture it.

288
00:32:51,370 --> 00:32:58,240
Such a powerful message out of that string. So. All right. Came out.

289
00:32:58,240 --> 00:33:00,910
He was quite upset how to do it.

290
00:33:00,950 --> 00:33:04,040
Suddenly there was one gentleman called Tanaji,

291
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:08,160
he had come to invite him for his son's wedding with his uncle.

292
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:15,040
And he saw him so upset he said, "Why are you so upset, sir?"

293
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:19,540
He said, "My mother has asked me such and such thing." He said, "All right, I'm going.

294
00:33:19,540 --> 00:33:23,830
You don't have to go, because we'll have many Tanaji's like me

295
00:33:23,870 --> 00:33:28,200
but we have only one Shivaji. I'm going to do it." He said, "But your son is going to marry."

296
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:33,830
He said, "First let my sword marry this fort,

297
00:33:33,870 --> 00:33:37,490
then I will marry my son." Such people we had also.

298
00:33:37,540 --> 00:33:42,660
Such sacrifice. Only on that rakhi. Think of that, only one rakhi!

299
00:33:42,700 --> 00:33:45,490
All right. They didn't know this girl, they didn't know her father,

300
00:33:45,540 --> 00:33:48,040
they didn't know anything about her, they had never seen her.

301
00:33:48,080 --> 00:33:54,870
Can you think of somebody who will do like this in modern times?

302
00:33:54,910 --> 00:33:58,490
We are supposed to be very evolved, powerful, great people.

303
00:33:58,540 --> 00:34:02,700
Even in the pictures we need not show it.

304
00:34:02,740 --> 00:34:05,280
Nobody will come to see such a film because

305
00:34:05,330 --> 00:34:11,290
they'll feel so low. And he went there

306
00:34:11,330 --> 00:34:20,120
and he used a kind of a big lizard which went and fixed the nails.

307
00:34:20,160 --> 00:34:28,410
With a rope he climbed up and they conquered and won that fort.

308
00:34:28,410 --> 00:34:32,370
It was decided that if they are successful they should lit fire

309
00:34:32,410 --> 00:34:35,240
which Shivaji can see and come down.

310
00:34:35,240 --> 00:34:37,160
He saw the fire early in the morning so went there.

311
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:41,660
And under a tree the dead body of this Tanaji was lying.

312
00:34:41,700 --> 00:34:49,580
He looked at it and he said, "We have got the fort but we have lost a lion."

313
00:34:49,620 --> 00:34:53,160
That's why it's called as the Fort of the Lion, Sinhagad,

314
00:34:53,200 --> 00:34:55,620
which you can see from My house very clearly.

315
00:34:55,620 --> 00:34:59,910
But these are the monuments of a small thing called a rakhi.

316
00:34:59,950 --> 00:35:09,700
A small symbol of expression

317
00:35:09,700 --> 00:35:16,620
that can capture forts after forts.

318
00:35:16,620 --> 00:35:24,080
Another one where -- I've told this story before but I'll repeat it today --

319
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:27,580
was when Alexander the Great arrested

320
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:34,660
one king called Puru. Alexander had married an Indian lady

321
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:43,490
and the great Alexander was in jail. That was the day of Vishnumaya.

322
00:35:43,490 --> 00:35:50,950
So she sent -- this lady was very clever, his wife -- she sent a rakhi

323
00:35:50,990 --> 00:35:58,200
in a small, little thali covered nicely to the King Puru.

324
00:35:58,240 --> 00:36:05,740
And, as the rituals are, that day this was presented to him. So he had to accept.

325
00:36:05,790 --> 00:36:10,790
If it is sent, you have to accept. A sister sends it with deliberations

326
00:36:10,830 --> 00:36:15,830
but you have to accept. And he accepted it, and it was tied.

327
00:36:15,870 --> 00:36:18,240
Then he said, "Who is my sister?"

328
00:36:18,240 --> 00:36:24,990
They said, "Your sister is the wife of Alexander." Said,

329
00:36:25,040 --> 00:36:29,280
"Oh God, that means I have arrested my own brother-in-law!"

330
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:31,910
Immediately becomes a brother-in-law, immediately.

331
00:36:31,950 --> 00:36:34,700
No marriage took place, nothing. He's a brother-in-law.

332
00:36:34,740 --> 00:36:43,200
He rushed to the jail, fell flat before the great emperor.

333
00:36:43,240 --> 00:36:46,950
He couldn't understand, "What's happening to Puru?

334
00:36:46,990 --> 00:36:51,950
Why did he do all this?" He said, "Sir, I am sorry", in his own language,

335
00:36:51,950 --> 00:36:54,700
"I'm sorry I didn't know you were my brother-in-law.

336
00:36:54,700 --> 00:36:58,280
I'm sorry whatever I've done. Will you forgive me?" and all that.

337
00:36:58,280 --> 00:37:04,790
And he brought him, asked him to sit on his throne.

338
00:37:04,790 --> 00:37:07,490
He couldn't understand, "What's this going on?"

339
00:37:07,540 --> 00:37:11,490
"Please." Made him sit there, garlanded him, did his aarti,

340
00:37:11,490 --> 00:37:19,290
gave him ornaments, gave him big garlands of diamonds and rubies and things,

341
00:37:19,330 --> 00:37:25,330
and touched his feet, washed his feet and then, with great honor, sent him home.

342
00:37:25,330 --> 00:37:27,280
He couldn't understand.

343
00:37:27,290 --> 00:37:29,830
"Has he gone mad or he's possessed by someone?"

344
00:37:29,830 --> 00:37:32,660
He must have thought, "Some Greek has possessed this fellow",

345
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:35,330
the way he was surrendering.

346
00:37:35,370 --> 00:37:41,080
When he went home his wife was smiling.

347
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:42,580
He said, "Why are you smiling?"

348
00:37:42,620 --> 00:37:46,080
She said, "I knew the trick will work with Indian mind."

349
00:37:46,120 --> 00:37:50,410
"What was the trick?" She showed him one string. "This was the trick."

350
00:37:50,450 --> 00:37:52,410
He couldn't understand, started looking at it.

351
00:37:52,450 --> 00:37:58,120
"What is this?" She said, "This is the rakhi. This is the thing I sent him.

352
00:37:58,120 --> 00:38:03,080
This has the symbol of a sister, that's how you're released."

353
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:05,620
Alexander sat back.

354
00:38:05,620 --> 00:38:11,660
He said, "Oh God, these people can release their enemies on a string?

355
00:38:11,700 --> 00:38:15,240
I can't capture these people. They are too good.

356
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:19,200
They are too subtle. These subtleties we cannot understand."

357
00:38:19,240 --> 00:38:22,700
And he turned back. But he took some poets with him

358
00:38:22,700 --> 00:38:27,700
who sang his praise, how he was, what a generous man.

359
00:38:27,700 --> 00:38:33,160
But I must say it is rather surprising to see such a subtle man in Greece.

360
00:38:33,200 --> 00:38:38,120
But maybe that was the time for them to understand subtleties,

361
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:40,330
but today I don't have much hopes.

362
00:38:40,370 --> 00:38:43,490
As I've seen them, they are not that subtle.

363
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:50,450
They only have people like Onassis who are their heroes, whom they worship.

364
00:38:50,490 --> 00:38:53,740
From where to what we have come? How we have used

365
00:38:53,790 --> 00:38:56,700
the same good things from horrible things now.

366
00:38:56,740 --> 00:39:00,280
How far we have gone. And I would say the same Vishnumaya

367
00:39:00,330 --> 00:39:03,700
has now put into this maya that you go to hell now,

368
00:39:03,740 --> 00:39:06,740
finished. It is She Who has arranged this point.

369
00:39:06,790 --> 00:39:11,080
She doesn't think that Americans deserve to be in Sahaja Yoga.

370
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:16,620
It is She Who's fighting Me. She says, "Mother, forget it, forget it, forget it!"

371
00:39:16,620 --> 00:39:20,700
See the films -- one worse than the other.

372
00:39:20,700 --> 00:39:25,540
You see the recent pictures, the modern ones, you can't even see them,

373
00:39:25,540 --> 00:39:29,120
you have to close your eyes. The same power now

374
00:39:29,160 --> 00:39:33,950
is for your destruction, used by you only.

375
00:39:33,950 --> 00:39:39,330
You are using it for your own destruction. All these films

376
00:39:39,370 --> 00:39:43,870
are working you out to fight each other,

377
00:39:43,910 --> 00:39:46,490
destroy each other, how to kill each other,

378
00:39:46,490 --> 00:39:50,700
how to be violent, how to be ugly, how to be shameless,

379
00:39:50,740 --> 00:39:54,040
how to have no self-respect, and no respect for others.

380
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:56,490
Is all coming through these medias.

381
00:39:56,540 --> 00:40:01,040
Your children are so rude. Nobody listens to anyone.

382
00:40:01,080 --> 00:40:08,290
Nobody respects their elders. If somebody is a simple, honest, intelligent,

383
00:40:08,330 --> 00:40:13,660
brilliant man, they think he's a fool because he doesn't know how to outwit you.

384
00:40:13,700 --> 00:40:16,080
He doesn't know how to talk sharply,

385
00:40:16,080 --> 00:40:19,200
because he doesn't know how to insult you all the time.

386
00:40:19,240 --> 00:40:25,740
The whole film industry is now working out how to coin

387
00:40:25,790 --> 00:40:29,700
more insulting words. The more insulting words there are,

388
00:40:29,700 --> 00:40:33,330
the better it is. And that's what the public wants,

389
00:40:33,370 --> 00:40:37,290
because now it has become a economic thing

390
00:40:37,330 --> 00:40:43,950
to use films for economic purposes. When money becomes everything --

391
00:40:43,950 --> 00:40:46,790
what is prostitution, you get money, what's wrong?

392
00:40:46,830 --> 00:40:48,620
What is wrong in destroying your family?

393
00:40:48,660 --> 00:40:50,450
You get money? It's all right.

394
00:40:50,450 --> 00:40:52,200
Now, are you going to take this money with you,

395
00:40:52,240 --> 00:40:55,950
or are you going to leave this barbaric children on this country?

396
00:40:55,990 --> 00:41:00,620
What are you going to achieve? And the money orientation is so much

397
00:41:00,660 --> 00:41:05,280
that people say that Americans are the most miserly people,

398
00:41:05,290 --> 00:41:11,540
they are very self-indulgent and the most miserly people, while here it is the Vishnumaya

399
00:41:11,540 --> 00:41:18,450
which is the most generous thing. She burns Herself off to give you light.

400
00:41:18,450 --> 00:41:24,790
And the miserliness also comes with money-orientation.

401
00:41:24,790 --> 00:41:28,790
They are also very mischievous,

402
00:41:28,830 --> 00:41:33,450
sometimes they try to play such tricks which are very heinous and horrible.

403
00:41:33,490 --> 00:41:41,280
Then electricity has to work and I don't know, I don't know about Her, how She'll work it out.

404
00:41:41,280 --> 00:41:45,830
But She's very angry, with Americans especially,

405
00:41:45,870 --> 00:41:49,990
because this is the country of Her Brother.

406
00:41:50,040 --> 00:41:55,370
This is the country where Her Brother rules, and She wants

407
00:41:55,410 --> 00:42:02,870
everything to be all right, because from here is generated all these nonsensical films

408
00:42:02,870 --> 00:42:07,580
nonsensical things which are destroying the whole world.

409
00:42:07,620 --> 00:42:13,540
AIDS is one of the blessings of Vishnumaya.

410
00:42:13,540 --> 00:42:17,910
It comes from Left Vishuddhi, people do not know.

411
00:42:17,950 --> 00:42:22,410
You start perspiring on the Left Vishuddhi to begin with.

412
00:42:22,450 --> 00:42:25,200
When people start feeling guilty,

413
00:42:25,200 --> 00:42:31,370
they should face it  and get rid of it.

414
00:42:31,410 --> 00:42:34,910
Of course it starts, as you say, with right sidedness.

415
00:42:34,950 --> 00:42:39,660
But this right sidedness ultimately ends up into Left Vishuddhi.

416
00:42:39,700 --> 00:42:43,660
And then the residual part of it starts generating.

417
00:42:43,660 --> 00:42:49,120
This kind of a weakness in a human being,

418
00:42:49,160 --> 00:42:54,830
because it is also the pure form of motherhood,

419
00:42:54,830 --> 00:43:01,240
is the Center Heart, is the pure form of motherhood.

420
00:43:01,280 --> 00:43:06,950
You see a child, you see a girl who is innocent. What interests her

421
00:43:06,990 --> 00:43:11,120
is her little dolly. She's the mother, out and out.

422
00:43:11,120 --> 00:43:16,790
If she's properly brought up, from very childhood she's a mother.

423
00:43:16,830 --> 00:43:22,540
And motherhood is the epitome of womanhood.

424
00:43:22,580 --> 00:43:25,950
There are some Sahaja Yogis also who are so stupid

425
00:43:25,950 --> 00:43:28,950
they don't want to have children after marriage.

426
00:43:28,950 --> 00:43:31,870
They should get out of Sahaja Yoga, immediately.

427
00:43:31,910 --> 00:43:35,950
We have not done all this to have people here

428
00:43:35,990 --> 00:43:39,700
who cannot produce children. If they can, they should.

429
00:43:39,700 --> 00:43:44,410
The reason is there are so many great souls who want to be born.

430
00:43:44,450 --> 00:43:50,370
These are the great fruits which are going to be prospering

431
00:43:50,370 --> 00:43:57,830
on the tree of your family life. And if you do not want to have any children,

432
00:43:57,830 --> 00:44:05,830
then what are you doing here? So the Vishnumaya's main thing

433
00:44:05,870 --> 00:44:14,450
is that a woman has to be a mother. Then that motherhood

434
00:44:14,490 --> 00:44:18,540
gives her that special capacity to shine.

435
00:44:18,580 --> 00:44:25,410
Now it starts with the Left Vishuddhi, the AIDS goes to the Center Heart.

436
00:44:25,450 --> 00:44:30,950
The Center Heart is challenged. The motherhood is lost.

437
00:44:30,990 --> 00:44:33,950
That's how the antibodies become weak.

438
00:44:33,990 --> 00:44:36,280
Once they are attacked, they become weak,

439
00:44:36,280 --> 00:44:41,660
they cannot fight the disease and that's how the person who gets AIDS

440
00:44:41,700 --> 00:44:48,240
has to face things in such a manner that it has no antibodies,

441
00:44:48,240 --> 00:44:56,410
so he becomes allergic to everything and he dies. To fight the AIDS,

442
00:44:56,450 --> 00:45:03,450
the sisters' and brothers' relations must be established

443
00:45:03,450 --> 00:45:07,280
so that sisters can look out for men,

444
00:45:07,280 --> 00:45:12,580
the way they are behaving, and they

445
00:45:12,620 --> 00:45:16,540
should look out for sisters, the way they are behaving.

446
00:45:16,540 --> 00:45:22,910
In this whole satanic movement I find

447
00:45:22,950 --> 00:45:25,950
the men become physically attacked

448
00:45:25,990 --> 00:45:31,120
and women become mentally attacked. And it's such an attack

449
00:45:31,120 --> 00:45:34,490
that women are difficult to get out of it.

450
00:45:34,540 --> 00:45:40,370
First of all, we have to decide what is our goal

451
00:45:40,410 --> 00:45:44,700
is to become the Spirit, and not a sex point.

452
00:45:44,700 --> 00:45:49,410
This maya has changed your goals completely.

453
00:45:49,410 --> 00:45:57,120
It's going to make you into worms or I don't know what else.

454
00:45:57,160 --> 00:46:00,790
Actually, this is what the Americans have to understand:

455
00:46:00,830 --> 00:46:04,990
where are they going? Everybody thinks that Americans

456
00:46:05,040 --> 00:46:07,990
are half-mad if not full-mad.

457
00:46:07,990 --> 00:46:10,950
Any American coming into any organization,

458
00:46:10,950 --> 00:46:14,290
"Oh, beware, American." Americans may not know about it.

459
00:46:14,330 --> 00:46:19,660
They never consider an American as a completely sane person.

460
00:46:19,700 --> 00:46:21,410
What is the reason? Because

461
00:46:21,410 --> 00:46:25,120
of this queer, weird, stupid ideas they have.

462
00:46:25,160 --> 00:46:33,700
But I heard that here the people claim that we have a fundamental right to be stupid and mad.

463
00:46:33,700 --> 00:46:41,580
This kind of a thing that is moving today in the country where you live,

464
00:46:41,580 --> 00:46:45,870
and if you have to save it, you have to turn their faces towards God.

465
00:46:45,910 --> 00:46:51,450
You have to turn their faces towards Self-Realization. And this is a very, very difficult task

466
00:46:51,490 --> 00:46:57,950
for which you all Sahaja Yogis, I request you and I pray for you,

467
00:46:57,990 --> 00:47:03,620
that you develop that kind of a power which is the Power of Vishnumaya

468
00:47:03,620 --> 00:47:06,280
that you shine with the Power of Vishnumaya.

469
00:47:06,290 --> 00:47:08,740
When I see your Statue of Liberty,

470
00:47:08,740 --> 00:47:11,200
I think she is the Vishnumaya  here standing.

471
00:47:11,240 --> 00:47:14,370
Why didn't they make a man stand there,

472
00:47:14,410 --> 00:47:21,410
why a woman? She is the symbol of the Sister, of Vishnumaya,

473
00:47:21,410 --> 00:47:24,080
and if you have to have your liberty, have it --

474
00:47:24,120 --> 00:47:28,910
but liberty of wisdom, not of stupidity.

475
00:47:28,950 --> 00:47:35,540
And this is what I have to tell you today in this great country of Shri Krishna,

476
00:47:35,580 --> 00:47:40,040
that you'd better be on the lookout. Better be on the lookout.

477
00:47:40,080 --> 00:47:47,410
You can say that She really rules in a proper way in South America,

478
00:47:47,410 --> 00:47:55,450
and that was Her domain, too. And there electricity is not so prevalent.

479
00:47:55,490 --> 00:48:01,040
But the perversion has started because they started producing cocaine

480
00:48:01,080 --> 00:48:04,160
and other horrible things to spoil your Left Vishuddhi.

481
00:48:04,200 --> 00:48:13,120
One feels guilty with one thing in the North America

482
00:48:13,120 --> 00:48:20,870
and another one makes it bad through cocaine, and is nicely transported here

483
00:48:20,910 --> 00:48:30,700
for you to spoil your Vishuddhi. This is an attack on Vishnumaya,

484
00:48:30,740 --> 00:48:34,700
another attack on Vishnumaya from the South

485
00:48:34,740 --> 00:48:38,490
because they are exporting. And once I asked them,

486
00:48:38,540 --> 00:48:40,540
"Why do you export it?" They said,

487
00:48:40,580 --> 00:48:43,740
"That is their lookout to save their people; it's not our lookout."

488
00:48:43,740 --> 00:48:48,490
In Colombia, officially. They feel that,

489
00:48:48,490 --> 00:48:51,160
"If the Americans cannot look after themselves,

490
00:48:51,200 --> 00:48:53,240
how can we look after our people?"

491
00:48:53,280 --> 00:48:57,660
And they're making a big money out of you because,

492
00:48:57,700 --> 00:49:00,290
"You paid so much attention to money. All right, have it.

493
00:49:00,330 --> 00:49:05,160
We'll also have money by giving you this horrible thing

494
00:49:05,160 --> 00:49:07,950
to spoil your Vishuddhis and take all your money,

495
00:49:07,990 --> 00:49:12,830
if you think money's that important." It's something, a very big play,

496
00:49:12,870 --> 00:49:17,040
it's a maya, it's a horrible maya into which this country has gone into.

497
00:49:17,080 --> 00:49:22,660
And you have to do it by shining examples

498
00:49:22,700 --> 00:49:28,280
to show how starkingly it is horrid

499
00:49:28,280 --> 00:49:31,490
the way we accept things so easily.

500
00:49:31,540 --> 00:49:36,040
I'm sure this Vishnumaya will crack certain nuts here

501
00:49:36,080 --> 00:49:41,990
and I hope it will create a new path for Sahaja Yogis to follow,

502
00:49:42,040 --> 00:49:44,410
to get more people into Sahaja Yoga

503
00:49:44,450 --> 00:49:48,830
in a proper, dynamic way and settle them in Sahaja Yoga.

504
00:49:48,870 --> 00:50:17,540
May God bless you.

505
00:50:17,540 --> 00:50:20,950
Before we start the Puja, I really admire the way

506
00:50:20,950 --> 00:50:23,990
you have created this maya here.

507
00:50:24,040 --> 00:50:30,290
I hope this will cover the blinding maya

508
00:50:30,330 --> 00:50:33,620
and put people into their right path.

509
00:50:33,660 --> 00:50:37,790
I must say I admire it, the way you have done it. It's beautifully done.

510
00:50:37,830 --> 00:50:40,580
May God bless you.

511
00:50:40,580 --> 00:51:45,910
One of the names of Devi is also Nirmala, because it means "pure",

512
00:51:45,950 --> 00:51:51,280
also these days people are talking of Khalsa and Khalistan.

513
00:51:51,280 --> 00:51:55,790
Khalis means "pure." Khalistan is the place

514
00:51:55,830 --> 00:51:59,620
where the pure people have to settle down, that is Sahaja Yogis.

515
00:51:59,660 --> 00:52:05,910
That's what was said that only the Khalis people, means the people who are pure

516
00:52:05,950 --> 00:52:11,910
have to form Khalistan, not those who are violent or those who are stupid.

517
00:52:11,950 --> 00:52:17,660
Is meant for the people who are Sahaja Yogis. Was said for the Sahaja Yogis.

518
00:52:17,700 --> 00:52:24,990
The saints would never tell that those violent people should have their Khalistan.

519
00:52:25,040 --> 00:52:31,740
So, as they call it "Nirmalites" are the Khalistani people and they are the Khalsas.

520
00:52:31,740 --> 00:52:37,950
Such a misnomer under the influence of Vishnumaya.

